# Committed regtest fixture: un-ignore LevelDB write-ahead logs (numeric-
# prefixed .log files) that the repo-wide *.log* rule would otherwise
# swallow. Scoped narrowly to the three LevelDB subdirs so bitcoind's own
# debug.log stays ignored.
!regtest/blocks/index/[0-9]*.log
!regtest/chainstate/[0-9]*.log
!regtest/indexes/txindex/[0-9]*.log
